21
00:01:49,933 --> 00:01:54,450
The SEC applies the Howey Test to determine if a token

22
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:59,751
is a security. Four criteria: investment of money, in a common

23
00:01:59,851 --> 00:02:05,907
enterprise, with expectation of profit, from the efforts of others. Most

24
00:02:06,007 --> 00:02:11,977
