and custodians — must be licensed with strict KYC and

35
00:03:10,198 --> 00:03:16,034
AML requirements. Stablecoins like USDC require EU banking licenses. The

36
00:03:16,134 --> 00:03:22,052
critical carve-out: protocols that are fully decentralized with no single

37
