controlling entity are explicitly excluded from MiCA. This means truly

38
00:03:27,922 --> 00:03:33,840
decentralized protocols like Uniswap are not directly regulated. NFTs are

39
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:40,270
not covered unless they function as financial instruments. Regulatory clarity,

40
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:45,876
even if initially burdensome, tends to be positive for institutional

41
00:03:45,976 --> 00:03:48,020
